  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="post-wrap post-body reveal">
<h2>Why do brands choose Viven as their video agency?</h2>
<p>Brands choose Viven as their video agency because it combines Swiss precision, strategic storytelling, and a streamlined production process to turn video into a measurable driver of sales and trust. According to HubSpot, 54% of consumers want to see more video content from brands they support, and 88% of video marketers report that video delivers a positive ROI.</p>
<h2>What Sets Viven Apart</h2>
<p>Viven combines technical expertise with a deep understanding of branding and sales strategy. We specialise in creating <a href={p("services/product-video")}>product videos</a> that showcase features while creating an emotional connection with the target audience, and our streamlined process ensures every project is delivered on time, within scope, and aligned with business objectives. Customers are 64% more likely to purchase a product after watching a product video, which is why we focus on videos that highlight product benefits in clear, engaging ways.</p>
<h2>Case Example: Meteomatics</h2>
<p>Meteomatics, a leading weather data solutions provider, partnered with Viven to create video content that simplified its complex services for a broader audience, including a series of explainer videos aimed at communicating its value proposition to existing and potential clients. After release, Meteomatics saw a significant increase in engagement, higher website traffic, and a notable expansion of its client base — see more examples in our <a href={p("projects")}>project portfolio</a>.</p>
<h2>Tailored Video Solutions for Every Stage of the Customer Journey</h2>
<p>Viven offers video solutions designed to move customers from awareness to purchase, including <a href={p("services/corporate-video")}>corporate videos</a> that build trust and credibility, explainer videos that clarify complex concepts, testimonial videos that reinforce social proof, and <a href={p("services/social-media-video")}>social media videos</a> that drive engagement and awareness.</p>
<h2>Precision-Driven Production for Global Brands</h2>
<p>Viven is based in Switzerland, a country known for precision and quality, and we bring that same attention to detail to every project. Our team of directors, editors, motion graphic designers, and video strategists manages every detail, from location scouting to post-production, for clients across industries such as luxury, finance, healthcare, and technology.</p>
<h2>Why Video Content Converts More Customers</h2>
<p>According to a 2023 Wyzowl study, 96% of people have watched an <a href={p("services/how-to-video")}>explainer video</a> to learn more about a product or service. Video increases comprehension and retention, leading to greater trust and a higher likelihood of purchase — insights we apply to produce content that accelerates decision-making and improves the overall customer experience.</p>
<h2>Why Brands Appoint Viven as Their Video Agency</h2>
<ul>
<li>Proven expertise in product video production</li>
<li>Customised strategies aligned with business objectives</li>
<li>Full-service production, from concept to delivery</li>
<li>Efficient workflows that respect time and budgets</li>
<li>Experience working with leading brands in Switzerland and globally</li>
</ul>
<p>Partnering with Viven as your video agency is a strategic decision that delivers results — our approach to video production helps brands connect with customers, build trust, and <a href={p("blog/boost-brand-growth-with-an-effective-video-marketing-strategy")}>accelerate growth through video marketing</a>. <a href={p("contact")}>Visit Viven</a> to learn how we can help you achieve your business goals through high-quality video content.</p>
